nodes.body: Dear @FR-vdash-bot, this PR provides speedups to mathlib, but there are also performance regressions. Besides that, the methodology for arriving at the changes you propose is not clear to me. Since this PR has not seen activity in a month, I am now closing this PR. If you would like to continue work on this PR, please feel free to reopen it.

I explained the plan on [Zulip](https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/287929-mathlib4/topic/Ways.20to.20speed.20up.20Mathlib). This is a necessary step to make the search for `Zero/One/Add/Mul` instances along `Zero/One/Add/Mul` -> `...` -> `Ring` -> `CommRing` -> `Field`. Maybe there are some alternative methods, but let's keep this PR open for now.
